\section{Data analysis and results of the 1999 $\rho$ -class observation}
\label{romode}

The temporal analysis of data in $\rho$ mode,  performed taking into account the results 
presented in Papers I and III, was focused on evaluating the recurrence 
time of the bursts and of the HXD. 

